Give users an identity to interact with our web or mobile app
cognito user pools: 
  sign in functionality wfor app users
  integrate with API gateway and ALB
Cognito Identity Pools
  provide AWS credentials to users so they can access AWS resources directly
  integrate with Cognito User Pools as an identity provider
Cognito = web/mobile hundreds, SAML, mobile

-------------------------------

CUP (User pool)

Create a serverless database of user for your web & mobile apps
simple loging
password reset
email and phone number verification
MFA
Federated identites
CPU integrates with API gateway and ALB

------------------------------

Federated Identities

Get identities for users so they obtain temporary AWS credentials
users source can be Cognitos User Pools, 3rd party
Users can then access AWS services directly or through API gateway
The IAM policies applied to the credentials are defined in cognito
they can be customized based on the user_id for fine grained control
Default IAM roles for authenticated and guest users

